Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.96,0:00:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we're going to make announcements.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.35,0:00:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody told me there was going to be a lot of people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.18,0:00:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.50,0:00:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.71,0:00:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning to all of you, and thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.59,0:01:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of your faces are very familiar to us, and some of you aren't,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.35,0:01:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,but we are so glad to see all of you here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.59,0:01:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And we hope that you enjoy the lecture,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.21,0:01:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and Doc has been preparing for it for the last three weeks,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.06,0:01:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,so you're going to be in for a treat.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.35,0:01:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I have a few announcements, so please go ahead and sit down,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.40,0:01:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and then I'll introduce Dave for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.01,0:01:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I need you to turn off all your cell phones,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.93,0:01:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and there's no recording or filming of the event,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.06,0:01:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,so please don't turn on your cell phones to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.45,0:01:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, I'd like to have the people that are from out of country.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.87,0:01:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you stand up?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.29,0:01:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone that's here from out of country?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.73,0:02:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.93,0:02:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.31,0:02:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that it's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.47,0:02:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a very difficult trip,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.21,0:02:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and it just shows that your spirituality is very important to you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.25,0:02:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,because you've come such a long distance to hear us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.90,0:02:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So now I'd like to introduce my husband,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.87,0:02:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Dr. David R. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.06,0:02:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a pointer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.61,0:02:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot a pointer, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.22,0:02:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You got a pointer?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.61,0:02:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.12,0:02:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.37,0:02:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, you got a pointer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.68,0:02:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what is the lecture on today?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.52,0:02:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Success.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.37,0:02:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Success?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.49,0:02:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, who the heck is interested in success?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.34,0:03:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I had the secret of success to announce to the group,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.37,0:03:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and I forget what the hell it was now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.94,0:03:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The secret of success, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.72,0:03:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember what we...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.94,0:03:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have a pointer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.68,0:03:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have a pointer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.74,0:03:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the secret of success, one, is to be prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.09,0:03:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Think through your project in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.83,0:03:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Step by step.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.91,0:03:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Some days are diamonds, and some days are dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.43,0:03:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we just thought you would enjoy that little demonstration
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.62,0:03:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,of the importance of taking your Thrive Project through in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.87,0:03:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, we have slides today,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.90,0:03:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and the purpose of these slides
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.40,0:04:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,is so I don't forget what we're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.13,0:04:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are the slides?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.59,0:04:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,101 Ways to Success.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.49,0:04:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we've had an interesting year so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.90,0:04:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We've had 101 days, 101 ways to happiness,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.80,0:04:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,101 ways to peace,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.98,0:04:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and we finish up the year with 101 ways to success.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.20,0:04:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if you've got peace, happiness, and success,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.88,0:04:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,you've pretty much depleted your earthly life of any challenges.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.00,0:04:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.57,0:04:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And you've got nothing left but serenity, if you can handle that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.10,0:04:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not too popular a thing anymore, but serenity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.48,0:04:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, how many people are here for the first time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.37,0:04:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,First time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.26,0:04:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,First time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.32,0:05:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,First time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.31,0:05:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.20,0:05:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.93,0:05:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we're going to discuss things that have come out of many years of research,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.52,0:05:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,many years of research.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.64,0:05:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,As well as 50 years of clinical experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.41,0:05:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I had the largest psychiatric practice in the United States for some 50 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.87,0:05:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we got into consciousness research.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.13,0:05:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And consciousness research really evolved because we discovered a basic truth
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.98,0:05:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,that is really devastating in its application.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.62,0:05:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And that is truth makes your body go strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.91,0:05:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Makes your body go strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.31,0:05:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And falsehood makes it go weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.88,0:05:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that ought to be pretty handy to know, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.42,0:06:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if you've got a friend, you've got a friend, and I've got a friend here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.04,0:06:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I'll say, if I ask something, you know, a question, and I'll say, okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.42,0:06:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,there's over 700 people sitting out there, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.07,0:06:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Over 800 people resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.36,0:06:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Over 850 resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.80,0:06:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So, there's between 800 and 850.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.33,0:06:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can instantly know the truth of anything in the universe,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.43,0:06:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,which is so devastating that practically nobody gets that when I tell you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.87,0:06:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Approximately 15% of this audience will get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.56,0:06:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The other 85, I don't know what happens to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.70,0:06:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha, ha, ha, ha, ha, ha, ha, ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.31,0:06:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We can track back through biologic history.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.24,0:06:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Why truth would have an attractive, that which is good for the organism would have a positive response.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.37,0:07:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That which would be poisonous and therefore contribute to your downfall would have a negative effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.50,0:07:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You look at the forms of early life, how would a little protozoa or an amoeba know what's good to eat or what would kill them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If you didn't know the difference, he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.11,0:07:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it was very important for...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.80,0:07:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The earliest life forms to know that which is pro and supportive of life and that which is negative and will kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.72,0:07:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So, those that didn't learn the lesson, many of them died by the billions over the centuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.75,0:07:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we're left with an organism, intrinsically this organism.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.43,0:07:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the nervous system, which is controlled by the field of consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.24,0:07:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.81,0:07:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the answer that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.63,0:08:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The answer that we get when we ask a question and press down on her arm is being answered by the field of consciousness itself and not by the person.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.08,0:08:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It has...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.73,0:08:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the answer has nothing to do with what this person here thinks the answer might be or this person here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.83,0:08:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this is therefore called consciousness research.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.75,0:08:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The infinite field of consciousness, what other...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.79,0:08:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,In other languaging...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.94,0:08:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,In conceptualization would be that you might say the mind of God out of which arises all of creation with no beginning and no ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.67,0:08:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The field of consciousness is infinitely powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.55,0:08:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It has no beginning and no ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.95,0:08:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And within the field of consciousness, there is neither here nor there, then or now, and all time is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.03,0:08:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,In the infinite field of consciousness, which you might call the mind of God,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.40,0:08:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,all time...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.88,0:09:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,All times are now, everywhere is right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.26,0:09:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I can ask a question of the field of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.28,0:09:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And the answer arises as though the event was...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.37,0:09:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It occurred right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.63,0:09:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I can ask, you know, what was the consciousness level of Napoleon, the Bonaparte?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.72,0:09:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It mattered before we met, before or after Waterloo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.44,0:09:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we'll demonstrate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.08,0:09:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,By the end of the day, we'll show you how to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.12,0:09:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.98,0:09:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,When I say, you can see I'm not using any suggestion because what I'm holding in mind, she does not know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.96,0:09:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And I can say to her, okay, I first ask this, the question I was asked right before this lecture, the answer is yes, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.20,0:10:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The answer is yes, we were asked to do a favor for somebody, and the answer is yes, we should go along with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.03,0:10:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, if it were a negative response or something like that, we would have gotten a no.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.80,0:10:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If it was illegal or untruthful, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.00,0:10:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so, it's very handy to be able to know the difference between truth and falsehood about anything, anywhere, anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.01,0:10:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And with it, I guarantee success.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.48,0:10:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I buy this car?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.51,0:10:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And her arm goes weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.75,0:10:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's a clunker.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.96,0:10:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I buy this car?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.01,0:10:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Arm goes strong, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.27,0:10:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.70,0:10:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we hire this employee?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.29,0:10:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes or no.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.78,0:11:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that you can know anything about anything is only grasped by 15% of the average audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.37,0:11:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes me sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.98,0:11:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I want the 85% who don't get it to listen carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.94,0:11:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.53,0:11:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I can ask, is what I'm holding in mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.04,0:11:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Is what I'm holding in mind truthful or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.49,0:11:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And press down on her arm, and if it's true, her arm goes strong, and if it's false, her arm goes weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.86,0:11:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,How can that be when she doesn't even know what question I'm holding in my mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.86,0:11:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What connects the two of us when we're not physically connected at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.37,0:11:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.94,0:12:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't know either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.24,0:12:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither of us know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.62,0:12:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.36,0:12:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we have...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.32,0:12:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I have hypothecated, of course, the infinite field of consciousness, but it's pragmatic value.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.65,0:12:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we're not here just for academic reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.03,0:12:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We're here for...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.84,0:12:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's of tremendous value.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.96,0:12:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's say you have a business, and you're thinking of opening a new branch in South America.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.65,0:12:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, you hold in mind this project, and you ask your partner,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.87,0:12:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,this is a practical idea that would be good to do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.88,0:12:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And you'll get a...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.54,0:12:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,A yes or a no.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.45,0:12:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If it says yes, you can go ahead with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.59,0:12:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If it says no, you can then ask further.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.75,0:12:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You can ask questions of why it wouldn't work now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.59,0:12:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're dumb and ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.88,0:12:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.66,0:13:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason you're a failure is because you're dumb and ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.05,0:13:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.67,0:13:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing wrong with being dumb and ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.51,0:13:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you can make millions of dollars being dumb and ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.05,0:13:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what people do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.14,0:13:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Run for Congress.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.19,0:13:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,All kinds of things you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.27,0:13:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We always joke about politicians.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.77,0:13:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you know, when you're a politician, you expect it, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.62,0:13:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.24,0:13:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this is a pointer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.79,0:13:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.29,0:13:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A laser.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.75,0:13:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to push it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.01,0:13:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,A laser pointer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.08,0:13:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to point it right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.70,0:13:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.92,0:13:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.66,0:13:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.94,0:13:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,One shot of that little red dot, and you're done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.78,0:14:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.30,0:14:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We started out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.04,0:14:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We evolved what is known as...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.30,0:14:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there an itch to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.47,0:14:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.53,0:14:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to fall off in the middle of a lecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.82,0:14:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What we evolved is a map of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.32,0:14:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A map of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.12,0:14:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And discovering what makes you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.25,0:14:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Truth makes you go strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.37,0:14:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We calibrated this field of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.01,0:14:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,which is inclusive of just about everything that's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.24,0:14:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's extremely useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.95,0:14:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,From this map of consciousness, you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.11,0:14:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,we calibrated...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.12,0:14:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We calibrated the level of consciousness of anything that is now or ever was,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.59,0:14:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,including all the people on the planet, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.50,0:14:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You find on a scale of one to a thousand,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.25,0:14:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,200 and over is truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.35,0:15:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,200 and over is the level of truth and integrity, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.76,0:15:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Below 200 are the levels of falsehood and the emotions that go with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.15,0:15:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, the emotions below 200 are scorn,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.08,0:15:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,hate, cravingness, anxiety, regret, despair,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.05,0:15:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,humiliation, and enslavement, withdrawal, despondency.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.37,0:15:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So when people go into a depression,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.20,0:15:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,what happens is they fall to the bottom of this scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.30,0:15:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,As we move up the scale of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.89,0:15:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,over the level of 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.72,0:15:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So many times when we calibrate something,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.94,0:15:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,we really want to know, is it over 200 or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.86,0:15:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true or is it false?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.03,0:15:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,200 and up, you go into the positive mental states,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.79,0:15:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,such as trust, optimism, forgiveness, understanding, reverence,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.17,0:15:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,serenity, and eventually bliss.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.94,0:16:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So these are the higher states.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.84,0:16:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, the highest states of all
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.58,0:16:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,are the advanced spiritual states leading to enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.75,0:16:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the level of enlightenment, you go from being courageous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.42,0:16:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, you let go of pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.95,0:16:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You let go of pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.54,0:16:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Pride is the big downfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.50,0:16:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Pride and anger and cravingness and fear and grief and guilt and shame
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.30,0:16:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,keep people in the bottom of the level.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.28,0:16:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Then when you face the truth about things and accept it,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.75,0:16:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,you develop courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.16,0:16:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you move to a level, a consciousness level 250,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.95,0:16:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,which is very comfortable, called neutrality.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.49,0:16:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,In neutral, it's okay if it happens and it's okay if it doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.83,0:16:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's say, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.07,0:16:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay if the audience gets it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.54,0:16:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.71,0:16:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's okay if they don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.00,0:16:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That gives you a certain independence, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.79,0:16:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,However, beyond that is willingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.53,0:17:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Willingness is my will for the audience is that they get it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.63,0:17:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So I move from 250 up to 310.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.83,0:17:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Willingness is the willingness to explain it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.18,0:17:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And accepting that this is necessary takes me up to reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.90,0:17:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So I use reason to explain things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.42,0:17:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, because I love this audience,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.44,0:17:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.85,0:17:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That moves you up to 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.52,0:17:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Then if I get that the audience is getting it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.23,0:17:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.15,0:17:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I move up to joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.40,0:17:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.05,0:17:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, then I end up at peace, 600.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.25,0:17:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And peace means that you're very happy how it all is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.88,0:17:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Some get it and some don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.29,0:17:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm at peace with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.29,0:17:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's okay if you don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.50,0:17:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't understand the thing I'm saying today,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.83,0:17:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,it's okay with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.59,0:17:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So you don't have to please me by getting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.50,0:18:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What a relief, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.77,0:18:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody's required to understand this at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.50,0:18:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, you're going to get it primarily by osmosis anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.88,0:18:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,When you get home, you'll say, what did he say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.79,0:18:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.11,0:18:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You get it by osmosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.70,0:18:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.05,0:18:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.14,0:18:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It means that the field,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.79,0:18:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the field generated by all of us here together
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.57,0:18:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,for the purpose for which we're here,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.00,0:18:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the field itself is enormously powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.53,0:18:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And groups such as AA, et cetera,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.94,0:18:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,they'll say, don't bother trying to get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.74,0:18:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Just go there and go to the meetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.01,0:18:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll get it by osmosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.33,0:18:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So all of you who don't get what I'm saying intellectually,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.31,0:18:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.16,0:18:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll get it by osmosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.09,0:18:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Good old osmosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.53,0:19:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,God counted on osmosis for the human condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.35,0:19:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He figures they're not going to get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.09,0:19:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll get it by osmosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.11,0:19:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So the presence of God then which prevails
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.94,0:19:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,has within it the power to bring understanding
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.31,0:19:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,to the human consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.98,0:19:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,without going through some linear logical sequence of thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.40,0:19:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So they won't necessarily go through,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.94,0:19:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,reason and logic,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.75,0:19:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,although we'll put it in there for those who are obsessive compulsive
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.94,0:19:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and want to know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.07,0:19:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It just is, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.27,0:19:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That should take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.75,0:19:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, now today we're talking about,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.01,0:19:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot what the subject was.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.38,0:19:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We're talking about,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.63,0:19:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,what were we talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.45,0:19:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, success, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.67,0:19:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it was something important, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.05,0:20:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so I'm doing,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.22,0:20:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,do a few remarks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.94,0:20:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to give you a few review slides.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.70,0:20:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the energy of the field of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.44,0:20:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And you see, as consciousness level moves higher and higher,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.31,0:20:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,you reach a point where it escalates.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.68,0:20:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And these are the divine states.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.07,0:20:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We seek out the company of the avatar,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.29,0:20:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,the great spiritual teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.18,0:20:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,because their aura radiates out this enormous energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.61,0:20:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The way you become enlightened,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.45,0:20:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,is you pick up from the consciousness of an enlightened being,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.91,0:20:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the energy, this energy field right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.19,0:20:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you see a little red dot?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.24,0:20:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.25,0:20:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.58,0:20:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.25,0:20:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,energy fuels of enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.84,0:20:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,See, this is love.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.80,0:20:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.17,0:20:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This is reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.26,0:20:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This is reason in the 400s.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.26,0:21:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Love is in the 500s.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.04,0:21:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Enlightenment is about 600.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.73,0:21:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,At 600, it's really a state of sort of bliss.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.66,0:21:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the very high advanced states of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.90,0:21:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,are infinitely powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.52,0:21:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And the way you reach the state yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.92,0:21:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,is somewhere in your life or lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.97,0:21:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The presence of the enlightened spiritual master
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.04,0:21:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,irradiates out this energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.78,0:21:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And you pick it up in your aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.00,0:21:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So, unfortunately,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.24,0:21:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't print it and can it and mail it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.60,0:21:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why people travel long distances.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.65,0:21:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the energy field of the aura of the teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.02,0:21:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,illuminates through your aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.46,0:21:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the way the Buddha transmitted enlightenment
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.20,0:21:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,was in silence
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.85,0:21:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,when he handed the flower to his follower.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.29,0:22:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The flower was only symbolic.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.57,0:22:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The follower,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.09,0:22:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and then I think it was,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.51,0:22:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,was picked up by the teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.00,0:22:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So, he picked up the energy field of the Buddha.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.40,0:22:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And then from him,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.33,0:22:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,that energy field was transmitted down
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.22,0:22:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,through the centuries,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.33,0:22:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,through the thousands and thousands of years.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.75,0:22:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So, in a way,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.59,0:22:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,we're all picking up the energy field of the Buddha.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.01,0:22:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you, Buddha.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.92,0:22:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Buddha who?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.75,0:22:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Buddha, Hanson, Johnson?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.29,0:22:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Buddha.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.16,0:22:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we're all picking up that energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.88,0:22:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,of originally released by the Buddha, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.48,0:22:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.77,0:22:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.04,0:22:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,how do you turn this thing on?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.91,0:22:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.03,0:22:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the consciousness level of mankind?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.74,0:22:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,People say, well, where's mankind?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.29,0:22:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The consciousness level of mankind right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.72,0:22:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,let's see if we have permission to do mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.09,0:22:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Mankind overall, we have permission to do, resist,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.81,0:23:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,is over 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.40,0:23:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, 205, 210, 209.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.81,0:23:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,208, 207.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.55,0:23:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Consciousness level of mankind is over 206, 205, 204.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.31,0:23:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Consciousness level of mankind right now is 204.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.48,0:23:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Truth is 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.75,0:23:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Mankind overall is at 204.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.57,0:23:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's do America.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.75,0:23:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to do America.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.57,0:23:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Consciousness level of America is over 400, 405, 406.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.66,0:23:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,America is about 405.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.35,0:23:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What did I say humankind was at, 204?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.44,0:23:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,204.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.27,0:23:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,204.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.77,0:23:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, we are very fortunate indeed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.29,0:23:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,to be living in a country
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.48,0:24:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,where the overall consciousness level
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.27,0:24:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,is much higher than mankind in general.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.81,0:24:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is a very advanced nation, you might say.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.98,0:24:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially California, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.65,0:24:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So 85% of the world's population,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.25,0:24:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,85% of the world's population calibrates below 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.09,0:24:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,200 is the level of truth and reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.90,0:24:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Truth and reality is at 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.25,0:24:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,85% of mankind calibrates below the level of truth
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.21,0:24:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and integrity, which explains and explains
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.34,0:24:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,why humanity is so fracture.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.80,0:24:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.75,0:24:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the nature of the nightly news and the world in all of its expressions as war
