Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.46,0:36:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,we expect things to be reasonable and to follow certain laws of logic
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.78,0:36:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and just jump from two plus two equals six
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.78,0:36:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and just jump from two plus two equals six
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.78,0:36:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,so there's certain laws of reason
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.78,0:36:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,alright let's go to the next
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.78,0:36:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,we could spend the whole morning just on this one chart
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.78,0:36:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,we could spend the whole morning just on this one chart
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.78,0:36:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,move to the next one
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.03,0:36:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,where is the next chart
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.03,0:36:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,now the functions of the mind
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.42,0:36:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought this would be somewhat interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.42,0:36:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,for later on because we're going to be talking about success
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.42,0:36:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,for later on because we're going to be talking about success
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.42,0:36:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the mind is really
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.38,0:36:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,there's really two levels of mind
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.38,0:36:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,there's what I call lower mind
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.38,0:36:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,lower mind
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.57,0:36:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,is somewhat limited
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.57,0:36:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,it's very personal
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.57,0:36:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.57,0:36:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,it's somewhat pedestrian
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.57,0:36:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.57,0:36:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,it has to do with physical and emotional
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.57,0:36:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,survival
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.86,0:36:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and acquisition
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.86,0:37:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,we're going to be talking about success today
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.86,0:37:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and so
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.86,0:37:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,part of lower mind is acquisition
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.86,0:37:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,some people conclude
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.15,0:37:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,that success is
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.25,0:37:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,represented by the accumulation
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.25,0:37:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,of things cars and houses
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.25,0:37:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and money and
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.25,0:37:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,accumulation of things
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.63,0:37:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,that's compared to higher mind
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.63,0:37:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,higher mind is more general
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.63,0:37:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and impersonal and unlimited
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.63,0:37:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,higher mind
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.76,0:37:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,is more detached
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.76,0:37:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,lower mind tends to take everything personally
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.76,0:37:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.15,0:37:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,they can't just criticize an idea
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.15,0:37:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,they have to attack the person
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.15,0:37:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,who has the idea
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.28,0:37:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,but higher mind
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.28,0:37:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,is more detached
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.28,0:37:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,it's really interested in whether
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.28,0:37:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,a thing is true or not
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.28,0:37:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,rather than attacking
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.28,0:37:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the person who says it
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.34,0:37:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,okay let's move on
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.53,0:37:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,that's enough background on all that
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.53,0:37:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,that's all
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.53,0:37:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,so lower mind then
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.53,0:38:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,is based on
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.53,0:38:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,desiring and wanting
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.53,0:38:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.53,0:38:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,tends to be somewhat gullible
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.53,0:38:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,tends to exploit life
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.53,0:38:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and we call it
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.53,0:38:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,we call them rather insensitive
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.53,0:38:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,people
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.75,0:38:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,the road to success
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.75,0:38:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,you have to awaken higher mind
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.75,0:38:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,higher mind is more intuitive
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.94,0:38:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,it's more expansive
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.94,0:38:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,it's interested in
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.94,0:38:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,aesthetics
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.94,0:38:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,art
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.94,0:38:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,how beautiful a thing is
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.57,0:38:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,it tends to serve life
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.57,0:38:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,lower mind tends to exploit life
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.57,0:38:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,higher mind tends to serve life
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.57,0:38:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,how can I serve you
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.57,0:38:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,how can I make something that mankind needs
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.57,0:38:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,so that's success
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.57,0:38:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,through adding to the value of human life
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.57,0:38:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,okay the next one
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.67,0:38:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah next thing
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.76,0:38:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,alright so
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.90,0:38:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,this has to do with the higher and lower mind
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.90,0:39:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,we're talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.48,0:39:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,brain physiology
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.48,0:39:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the brain physiology
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.94,0:39:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the left brain is the animal brain
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.38,0:39:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's very emotional
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.38,0:39:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,it goes through the thalamus
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.38,0:39:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,which is the emotional
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.38,0:39:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,center of the brain
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.38,0:39:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and you end up with an emotional
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.38,0:39:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,reaction
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.76,0:39:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,below
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.46,0:39:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,that's below 200
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.55,0:39:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness level above 200
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.55,0:39:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,is right brain
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.55,0:39:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,whereas left brain
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.76,0:39:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,releases adrenaline
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.76,0:39:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and the emergency emotions
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.76,0:39:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the right brain
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.76,0:39:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,releases endorphins
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.76,0:39:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,so
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.76,0:39:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,people that are spiritually oriented
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.76,0:39:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,then what happens
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.76,0:39:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,is the dominance of their brain
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.76,0:39:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,moves from the left side
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.76,0:39:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,which is the emotional emotion
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.76,0:39:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,greed, rage, hatred
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.76,0:39:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,getting even and vengefulness
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.76,0:39:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,moves to the right brain
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.76,0:39:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and the right brain dominance
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.76,0:40:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,is non-linear
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.76,0:40:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and positive emotion
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.76,0:40:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.76,0:40:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,people who are spiritually oriented
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.76,0:40:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,then have greater
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.76,0:40:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,greater immunity
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.76,0:40:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,have greater capacity for healing
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.03,0:40:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,they have a balanced acupuncture system
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.03,0:40:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.03,0:40:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,they give you a positive muscle test response
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.03,0:40:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,so when I ask her something that's true
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.03,0:40:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,her arm goes strong
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.03,0:40:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and something that's false
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.03,0:40:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,her arm goes weak
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.03,0:40:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,okay what's the next one
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.78,0:40:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,alright
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.38,0:40:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,social problems are attributed
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.38,0:40:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,to all kinds of things in society
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.63,0:40:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,all kinds of things in society
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.73,0:40:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,are given the blame
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.73,0:40:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that's the basis of
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.00,0:40:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,what's his name
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.00,0:40:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot his name
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.21,0:40:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,that's the basis of communism
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.86,0:40:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,is
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.86,0:40:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,everything is laid to blame
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.86,0:40:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,it sees cause and effect out there
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.86,0:41:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Karl Marx
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.86,0:41:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,then
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.96,0:41:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates slow because
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.96,0:41:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,it creates a dichotomy
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.46,0:41:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the cause is out there
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.59,0:41:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,now if the cause is out there
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.59,0:41:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,we examine that to see
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.59,0:41:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,where is the source of happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.59,0:41:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,anyway
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.98,0:41:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,well we found that the level of
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.98,0:41:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness of an individual
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.98,0:41:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,or a country or a company
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.98,0:41:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,here's the
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.17,0:41:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,people in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.17,0:41:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,who have a calibrated level of
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.17,0:41:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,100 to 200
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.28,0:41:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the rate of unemployment is 50%
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.28,0:41:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,not due to local
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.48,0:41:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,socio-economic conditions
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.48,0:41:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,but due to the fact that
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.48,0:41:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,that's their level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.55,0:41:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,the rate of poverty
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.55,0:41:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,at that level is 22%
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.55,0:41:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the happiness rate
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.80,0:41:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,people you say
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.80,0:41:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,people at this level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.80,0:41:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,are happy
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.84,0:41:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,15%
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.32,0:42:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and we find that the rate of criminality
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.32,0:42:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,is 50%
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.98,0:42:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,so we see that
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.98,0:42:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,cultural phenomena
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.32,0:42:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,which we deplore
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.32,0:42:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.32,0:42:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,we imagine that they're caused by
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.32,0:42:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,something out there
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.32,0:42:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,we find out that what it's really
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.32,0:42:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,associated with is a level of
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.32,0:42:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.42,0:42:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I lived through all kinds of depressions
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.42,0:42:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and eras when there was no jobs
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.42,0:42:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,there was no jobs at all
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.59,0:42:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,there was no jobs during the depression
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.59,0:42:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,my childhood
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.59,0:42:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,there was no jobs after World War II
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.59,0:42:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,when all the vets came home
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.59,0:42:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,there was no jobs anywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.59,0:42:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,where there was no jobs
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.59,0:42:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I always have two or three
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.59,0:42:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,how can I have two or three jobs
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.59,0:42:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,if the problem is in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.59,0:42:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's joblessness
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.09,0:42:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a bartender in the afternoon
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.09,0:42:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and a cab driver at night
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.26,0:42:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,what's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.51,0:42:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.63,0:42:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,then is
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.63,0:43:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,more important than anything
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.63,0:43:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,so people's education
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.63,0:43:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,people's education
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.63,0:43:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the quality of their
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.80,0:43:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,upbringing is of extreme
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.80,0:43:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,importance
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.84,0:43:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,the rate of criminality
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.84,0:43:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,as you can see
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.84,0:43:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,at the lowest levels of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.84,0:43:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,is very close to 100%
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.53,0:43:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,they're let out of prison
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.53,0:43:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and they commit a crime
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.53,0:43:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,within an hour
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.53,0:43:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.53,0:43:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,guys would go after
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.53,0:43:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,young children and all that
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.59,0:43:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,we'd let them out at 3 o'clock
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.59,0:43:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and by 4 o'clock they'd been arrested
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.59,0:43:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,they went to the nearest park
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.71,0:43:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,what does a pedophile do
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.71,0:43:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,when you let them out of prison?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.71,0:43:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,he heads to the nearest park
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.71,0:43:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and grabs the first kid he can grab
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.71,0:43:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,takes him less than an hour
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.71,0:43:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,people are surprised
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.32,0:43:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,by the rate of recidivism
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.32,0:43:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,what does a pedophile
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.48,0:43:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,think about in jail?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.48,0:44:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,what's the next little child
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.48,0:44:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,he's gonna grab in the park?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.63,0:44:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,what do you think he's thinking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.48,0:44:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Plato?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.36,0:44:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,alright, next move
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.51,0:44:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,levels of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.51,0:44:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and rate of happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.51,0:44:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,you see if happiness was in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.51,0:44:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,then we would see a correlation
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.51,0:44:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,but here what we see
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.51,0:44:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,is that the level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.51,0:44:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,is related to the rate of happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.51,0:44:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,if the
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.51,0:44:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,the number of people
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.51,0:44:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,who calibrate at 30
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.51,0:44:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,what percent are happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.51,0:44:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,4%
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.51,0:44:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,so the rate of happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.51,0:44:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,is related to the level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.51,0:44:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,below 200
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.51,0:44:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,the rate of happiness is
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.51,0:44:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,small
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.76,0:44:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,as we move up
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.76,0:44:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if you can see this pointer
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.76,0:44:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,it doesn't seem to do much pointing
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.76,0:44:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,but anyway
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.76,0:44:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,as you move up the level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.76,0:44:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,you see the percent of people who are happy
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.76,0:45:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,becomes
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.76,0:45:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,eventually predominant
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.76,0:45:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,if you're courageous
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.03,0:45:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,if you're in neutral
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.03,0:45:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,neutral is a nice place to be
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.03,0:45:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,uh
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.05,0:45:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,neutral at 250
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.05,0:45:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,it's okay if you get it
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.05,0:45:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,get the job and it's okay if you don't
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.05,0:45:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,willingness is
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.11,0:45:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,more positive
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.11,0:45:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,acceptance and then you're dominated by reason
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.11,0:45:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and eventually you reach
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.11,0:45:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,a state of lovingness
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.11,0:45:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and this is a possible state
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.11,0:45:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,for all of us within the world
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.11,0:45:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,uh
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.11,0:45:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,peace joy and enlightenment are
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.11,0:45:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,not necessarily available to everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.11,0:45:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,but lovingness
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.11,0:45:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,lovingness which is really an inner decision
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.11,0:45:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,at consciousness level
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.11,0:45:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,500
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.11,0:45:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the percent of people who reach 500
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.11,0:45:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,that are happy are about 90%
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.11,0:45:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,this is probably
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.48,0:45:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,the most important decision to make
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.48,0:45:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,is
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.63,0:45:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,lovingness
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.94,0:46:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,okay this is within
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.92,0:46:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,your capacity
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.92,0:46:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to make a decision
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.30,0:46:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't have to go away to school
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.30,0:46:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't have to study it
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.32,0:46:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't have to hear a lecture on it
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.32,0:46:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,there's a decision within yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.59,0:46:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,to be loving
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.59,0:46:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,towards all of life
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.59,0:46:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter what
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.42,0:46:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the fact that you don't understand it
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.42,0:46:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't get you off the hook
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.48,0:46:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,the decision to be loving
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.48,0:46:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,lovingness
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.48,0:46:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,towards all of life
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.48,0:46:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and all of its expressions
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.61,0:46:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,so as you walk along
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.61,0:46:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,you see a bug on the sidewalk
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.84,0:46:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,most of the people in this room
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.84,0:46:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,will walk over the bug
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.84,0:46:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the people that were just
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.32,0:46:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,let out of jail half an hour ago
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.32,0:46:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,will stamp on the bug
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.32,0:46:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,that's a huge difference
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.32,0:46:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,whether you stamp on the bug
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.32,0:46:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,or you wish the bug happy life
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.32,0:47:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and walk over it
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.01,0:47:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,so I want everybody here to pledge
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.01,0:47:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,no more bug stomping
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.01,0:47:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,after this lecture
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.84,0:47:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,when you see a little bug on the sidewalk
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.84,0:47:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,you say oh little bug
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.96,0:47:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad that you're around
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.57,0:47:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,created by God
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.57,0:47:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the universe is created by divinity
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.57,0:47:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and divinity is now expressing itself
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.57,0:47:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,as a bug on the sidewalk
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.61,0:47:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,whose little life is up to you
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.11,0:47:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,his whole life is up to you
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.11,0:47:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,your life
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.76,0:47:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,his life is up to you
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.76,0:47:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,what kind of a human being you have become
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.13,0:47:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,to become as loving
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.13,0:47:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,as we can be towards everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.67,0:47:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,to be loving means
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.67,0:47:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,that you tend to become forgiving
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.90,0:47:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,it means that you try to see everything
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.90,0:47:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,as the other person sees it
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.90,0:47:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see that
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.90,0:48:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I can understand why they're that way
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.90,0:48:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,because they were brought up in a certain way
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.90,0:48:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.90,0:48:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,the willingness to forgive
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.15,0:48:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember after World War II
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.15,0:48:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,you know
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.15,0:48:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,here the Japanese were shooting us down here
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.15,0:48:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I was out in the South Pacific
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.71,0:48:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,as soon as the war is over
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.71,0:48:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,we forgave each other like that
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.73,0:48:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,forgave each other instantly
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.73,0:48:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I said
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.09,0:48:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,salute them
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.09,0:48:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,we used to salute each other
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.09,0:48:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,because they were very very brave
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.09,0:48:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,these kamikazes were very
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.09,0:48:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,they were terrifying
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.09,0:48:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,kamikaze would fly right into you
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.09,0:48:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and blow up your ship and blow you up
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.09,0:48:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't give a damn that it blew him up
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.09,0:48:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,he just went to heaven
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.11,0:48:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,that's scary
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.15,0:48:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,so it's funny
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.82,0:48:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,after the war was over
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.82,0:48:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't take more than a couple of minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.11,0:48:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,to let go of the whole thing
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.11,0:48:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and after the war was over we'd shake the hands of the Jap aviators
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.11,0:48:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'd say no you guys were really great
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.11,0:48:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and we would shake hands
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.15,0:49:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,he was a great warrior
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.15,0:49:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and I gave him respect
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.15,0:49:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,for his incredible courage
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.21,0:49:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,in the name of the Emperor
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.21,0:49:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,in the name of the Sun God
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.21,0:49:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,really
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.21,0:49:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,he was serving the Sun God as he understood him
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.21,0:49:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and he flew right into us
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.21,0:49:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and would blow us right up
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.46,0:49:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and of course we were doing what we could do
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.46,0:49:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and the other thing that
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.03,0:49:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,backed us all up
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.03,0:49:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,is that we risked our lives for our buddies
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.03,0:49:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,so out of love
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.03,0:49:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,out of love
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.11,0:49:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,you'd walk into a hail of bullets
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.11,0:49:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,you'd walk in
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.11,0:49:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,very dangerous places
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.11,0:49:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,some of the places we went
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.11,0:49:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,we must have been cuckoo
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.11,0:49:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,but anyway
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.11,0:49:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,you did it out of love for your fellow man
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.26,0:49:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,so love your fellow man
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.26,0:49:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,is a very very powerful force
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.26,0:49:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's a lot different than
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.26,0:49:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,being ooh la la
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.26,0:49:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,what do they call them
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.48,0:49:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,the woo woos
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.48,0:49:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,in Sedona they call them the woo woos
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.48,0:50:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,the woo woos
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.65,0:50:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,talking about this
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.09,0:50:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,ooey gooey kind of
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.09,0:50:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,divine love and all sir
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.09,0:50:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.09,0:50:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,unless you bump into their
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.09,0:50:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,fender in the parking lot
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.09,0:50:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and instantly all that goo goo ha ha
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.09,0:50:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,son of a bitch I'm going to call my lawyer
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.09,0:50:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,they revert to
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.09,0:50:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,they revert to
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.09,0:50:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,what they really are
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.09,0:50:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,alright so
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.98,0:50:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the person who's
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.98,0:50:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,at 500
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.98,0:50:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,if somebody bumps into your fender
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.98,0:50:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's happened to me
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.98,0:50:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,he got backed right into my thing
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.98,0:50:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,in the parking lot
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.98,0:50:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,he backed in by mistake
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.98,0:50:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and dented an offender
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.98,0:50:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,he got all upset
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.98,0:50:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,he expected me to holler and shriek at him
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.98,0:50:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and I said look you can't help it
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.98,0:50:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,you drive a car enough miles
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.98,0:50:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,it's got to happen sooner or later
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.98,0:50:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I was really interested in calming this person down
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.98,0:50:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,so he didn't feel upset
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.98,0:50:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no point to feel upset I mean the dent is there already
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.98,0:51:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I got insurance
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.98,0:51:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,don't worry about it
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.98,0:51:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and I gave him a pat on the back
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.98,0:51:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,he was so relieved he almost fell over
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.98,0:51:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,he thought I was going to punch him in the nose or something
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.23,0:51:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,so love then is a very formidable
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.23,0:51:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,state
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.23,0:51:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,love will take you through all kinds of things
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.23,0:51:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,world wars and automobile accidents
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.23,0:51:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,family catastrophes
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.00,0:51:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,love at 500
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.00,0:51:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,is a very powerful energy
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.00,0:51:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and as time goes on
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.00,0:51:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the love becomes more progressively
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.00,0:51:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,more unconditional
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.00,0:51:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,unconditional
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.00,0:51:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,it means that you love things
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.00,0:51:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,initially you love things
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.00,0:51:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,without qualification
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.00,0:51:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't have to know all about
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.00,0:51:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,whether it's worthy of love
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.00,0:51:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,deserving of love
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.00,0:51:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,just you love all of life
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.00,0:51:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and all of its expressions
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.00,0:51:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,because it is
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.23,0:51:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,because it is
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.23,0:51:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,wow that doesn't take too much qualification
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.55,0:51:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,why should I love everybody in this audience
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.25,0:52:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,because you are
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.11,0:52:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,because you are here on top of me
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.11,0:52:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,you not only are
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.11,0:52:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,you are here
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.11,0:52:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,that makes it doubly neat
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.11,0:52:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,you love things
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.30,0:52:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,because they exist
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.30,0:52:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,so the source then
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.36,0:52:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,for your love of things
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.36,0:52:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,is strictly their existence
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.36,0:52:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and their existence is up to the will of God
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.36,0:52:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,so
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.36,0:52:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter what you love
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.36,0:52:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,you are loving some expression of God
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.36,0:52:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and one day as you are walking down the street
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.36,0:52:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,the divinity of all things
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.36,0:52:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,shines forth
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.63,0:52:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and you are never the same again
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.63,0:52:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the divinity of all things
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.92,0:52:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,shines forth
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.92,0:52:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and you can see its incredible beauty
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.92,0:52:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,this is arranged for the convenience
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.36,0:52:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,of those of us who are stupid
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.36,0:52:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and can't see beauty unless it is
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.36,0:52:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,completely arranged for us
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.09,0:52:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,even the stupid can see the beauty
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.09,0:52:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,of God's rose
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.50,0:53:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,so nothing has to meet
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.50,0:53:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,any kind of a qualification
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.50,0:53:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,to justify
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.53,0:53:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,our lovingness for it
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.53,0:53:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore the downfallen
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.59,0:53:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,we can
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.78,0:53:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,love them without being
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.78,0:53:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,naively trusting towards them
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.78,0:53:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the black mamba
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.94,0:53:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,will do you in
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.94,0:53:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the minute it gets a chance
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.94,0:53:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,so
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.42,0:53:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,you can love the black mamba for what it is
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.42,0:53:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,but only an idiot
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.42,0:53:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,would let him out of the cage
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.42,0:53:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,which is a story I've told before
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.59,0:53:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,about a friend of mine
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.59,0:53:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,who had a pet black mamba
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.59,0:53:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he was doing LSD
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.59,0:53:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,at the time but anyway
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.59,0:53:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,he had a pet mamba
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.59,0:53:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,so this black mamba
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.59,0:53:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,black mamba says to him
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.65,0:53:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,all of a sudden speaks to him
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.65,0:53:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and says
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.65,0:53:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,you can let me out of here
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.65,0:53:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't hurt you
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.03,0:53:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,please let me out
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.03,0:54:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like being in this cage
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.03,0:54:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,please let me out
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.03,0:54:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise you I won't hurt you
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.32,0:54:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,so this friend of mine
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.32,0:54:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,called all of his friends
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.32,0:54:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and this black mamba says to me
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.32,0:54:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,if I let him out of the cage
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.32,0:54:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,he won't hurt me
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.32,0:54:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,so his friend says to him
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.32,0:54:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,don't believe him he's lying
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.32,0:54:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,don't believe him he's lying
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.32,0:54:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's so funny
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.32,0:54:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,alright
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.32,0:54:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,where are we now
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.40,0:54:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,so here's where the
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.40,0:54:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,levels of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.40,0:54:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and the rate of happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.40,0:54:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,you can see that people who live
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.40,0:54:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,at 500
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.40,0:54:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the chances of being happy
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.40,0:54:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,are about 90%
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.40,0:54:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and the other 10%
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.40,0:54:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,may have specific reasons
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.40,0:54:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,within their personal lives
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.40,0:54:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what the limitation is
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.40,0:54:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,when I used to see people in the office
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.40,0:54:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I would know what the limitation was
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.40,0:55:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and try and work them around that limitation
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.40,0:55:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,very often
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.40,0:55:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,a resentment from childhood
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.40,0:55:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,something their mother did
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.40,0:55:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,or their father did or said
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.40,0:55:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and they are carrying this resentment
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.40,0:55:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and forgiveness then
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.40,0:55:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,is very important
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.40,0:55:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,sooner or later
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.40,0:55:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,to forgive everybody and anything
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.40,0:55:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,how can you forgive people
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.40,0:55:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,who have done stupid ignorant cruel
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.51,0:55:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and injurious things to you
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.51,0:55:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,you forgive them because you see them as limited
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.51,0:55:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,they didn't know any better
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.51,0:55:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,they didn't know any better
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.51,0:55:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,for the same reason then
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.51,0:55:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,that you forgive a dog who bites you
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.51,0:55:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,if you put your hand in the car
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.51,0:55:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,with a dog in it
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.51,0:55:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,the dog will bite you
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.51,0:55:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,that happened to somebody I knew
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.51,0:55:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the dog was just doing his doggy thing
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.59,0:55:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,he was supposed to protect his car
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.59,0:55:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and some idiot is trying to
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.59,0:55:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,invade his car as far as he was concerned
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.59,0:55:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,so in each case where there is an exception
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.59,0:55:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,to the rule you will find
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.59,0:55:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,that there is a particular reason
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.78,0:56:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,let's move to the next one
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.78,0:56:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,yes, ok
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.88,0:56:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,we use the calibrated levels of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.71,0:56:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,to calibrate
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.71,0:56:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual teachers
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.71,0:56:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,throughout history
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.71,0:56:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,people are always calling
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.71,0:56:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,our office and sending us emails
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.71,0:56:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,about the calibration level
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.71,0:56:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,of various teachers
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.71,0:56:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,so we thought it was much easier
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.71,0:56:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,just to publish the best known
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.71,0:56:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,because they are very well represented
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.71,0:56:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,throughout time
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.96,0:56:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.53,0:56:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual literature of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.53,0:56:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,so
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.59,0:56:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,when they ask about
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.59,0:56:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,a local teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.59,0:56:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,a lot of times they will ask me
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.59,0:56:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,what about
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.59,0:56:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Swami Bum Bum
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.59,0:56:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,he is about 80
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.59,0:56:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,probably rape you
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.59,0:56:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,if you didn't keep your eyes open
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.67,0:56:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,so anyway we thought
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.67,0:56:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,just for comparison
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.67,0:56:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,because there are a lot of pseudo gurus around
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.67,0:56:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,really bad actors to tell you the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.67,0:57:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and I don't know why they are so attracted
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.67,0:57:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,to pedophilia
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.67,0:57:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,you see pedophilia seems to be very big
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.67,0:57:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,amongst fallen spiritual teachers
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.67,0:57:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I can never find anything sexually attractive
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.67,0:57:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,about a child
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.67,0:57:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,so there is something demented about them
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.67,0:57:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,alright we move on to the next one
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.67,0:57:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual teachers continued
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.07,0:57:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,we will move on from there
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.07,0:57:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,anyway all I want people to know
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.11,0:57:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,is that there are
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.11,0:57:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,over a hundred
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.11,0:57:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,if people are looking for a good teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.11,0:57:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,there is over a hundred
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.11,0:57:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,who are calibrated very high
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.11,0:57:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,let's move to the next one
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.59,0:57:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,here you have today's world
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.59,0:57:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,laid out for you
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.63,0:57:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,here is today's world folks
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.67,0:57:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,there they are
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.94,0:57:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,trust me
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.59,0:57:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,trust me
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.09,0:57:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,trust me America
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.09,0:57:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,trust me voter
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.09,0:58:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,trust me investor
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.44,0:58:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,now so this is
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.44,0:58:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,the importance of this
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.44,0:58:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,is the difference between perception
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.67,0:58:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and reality
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.67,0:58:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,perception is
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.67,0:58:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,what you think you see
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.67,0:58:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,so what you see out there
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.67,0:58:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,is what you think exists
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.67,0:58:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,so
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.67,0:58:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the more spiritually sophisticated
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.67,0:58:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,person sees past appearance
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.67,0:58:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and moves into essence
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.67,0:58:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care what the
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.86,0:58:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,appearance of a thing is
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.86,0:58:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know what the essence of it is
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.86,0:58:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.86,0:58:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care that it's a sleek looking airplanes
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.86,0:58:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to make sure the wings hang on
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.86,0:58:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,until we land
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.86,0:58:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,so if I calibrate an airplane
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.28,0:58:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and it comes out at 190
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.28,0:58:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to take the next plane out
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.28,0:58:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,one time they used to have a shuttle
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.84,0:58:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,between Washington DC
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.84,0:58:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and New York City
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.03,0:58:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and I used to go to some meeting in Washington
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.03,0:58:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I forget
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.03,0:59:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and they guaranteed every hour on the hour
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.03,0:59:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,there would be a plane
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.03,0:59:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,so at midnight one time
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.03,0:59:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I get there at midnight
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.03,0:59:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and there was one person
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.03,0:59:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,me
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.30,0:59:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,in Washington DC
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.30,0:59:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,so the airline said if they had one passenger
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.30,0:59:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,they would fly it
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.30,0:59:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,so at midnight I'm the only passenger on this plane
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.30,0:59:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,they ran a whole plane from Washington DC
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.30,0:59:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to New York City
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.30,0:59:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,because of me
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.30,0:59:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,so I hear I'm on this plane
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.30,0:59:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,all by myself
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.30,0:59:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,there's nobody on this plane but me
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.30,0:59:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess the pilots up in front
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.30,0:59:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,but there's nobody around
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.30,0:59:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,they didn't have a stewardess for passenger one
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.61,0:59:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,so I'm flying all alone in the dark
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.61,0:59:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm looking down
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.61,0:59:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I see the city's down below
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.61,0:59:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and I get
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.61,0:59:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,you are the only person on this plane
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.61,0:59:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,the only one
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.61,0:59:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,uh oh
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.61,0:59:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,well God
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.71,0:59:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,is there some message I'm supposed to be getting?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.71,0:59:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,so I quickly said my prayers
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.71,1:00:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured there could be a reason
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.71,1:00:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,there was only just one of us
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.71,1:00:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,alright we'll move on
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.71,1:00:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,so here we're
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.44,1:00:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,talking about success
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.44,1:00:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,101 ways to success
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.32,1:00:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the earlier lectures we did so far this year
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.32,1:00:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,101 ways to peace and to happiness
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.32,1:00:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,so peace and happiness
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.32,1:00:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and then eventually
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.32,1:00:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,these bring you to success
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.32,1:00:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,people think that
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.40,1:00:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,peace and happiness
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.40,1:00:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,have to be sacrificed for success
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.40,1:00:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,uh no
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.40,1:00:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,peace and happiness
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.40,1:00:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,are part and parcel of success
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.40,1:00:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,true success means you're pleased
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.40,1:00:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,with how it's all going etc
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.40,1:00:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,so we're talking today
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.59,1:00:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,about success
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.59,1:00:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and how simple it is
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.15,1:00:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,so we have to first define
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.30,1:00:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,what it is
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.30,1:00:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,well there's internal success
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.30,1:00:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very pleased with something
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.30,1:00:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and then there's external success
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.30,1:00:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,as the world views it
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.34,1:00:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm working on success
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.34,1:01:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,you mean within yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.34,1:01:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,you can be very pleased
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.34,1:01:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,you know how you saw a piece of wood
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.34,1:01:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,or how you planted your garden
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.34,1:01:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,but the world wouldn't consider that success
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.34,1:01:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,so you have to decide
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.34,1:01:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,do you mean internal or external
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.34,1:01:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,which are you aiming at
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.34,1:01:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,are you aiming at being pleased
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.34,1:01:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,with your own self
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.63,1:01:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the hardest critic
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.63,1:01:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to deal with
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.63,1:01:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,is Dave
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.63,1:01:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,he's the only one I gotta please
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.63,1:01:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and if it doesn't turn out right
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.63,1:01:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,no rest
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.92,1:01:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,go back to your desk
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.92,1:01:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and work on it some more
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.55,1:01:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,internal so success then
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.55,1:01:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,is either within yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.55,1:01:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,what you consider to be success
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.55,1:01:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,a resolution of a project
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.55,1:01:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,you've set up for yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.55,1:01:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and then there's external success
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.55,1:01:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,as the world views it
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.55,1:01:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,what the world views
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.55,1:01:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,as success
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.61,1:01:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,is a different animal
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.61,1:01:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,than what I consider to be success
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.61,1:02:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,success means to me
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.61,1:02:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,that if I sit down
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.61,1:02:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,to write 101 ways to success
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.61,1:02:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I write 101 ways to success
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.61,1:02:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.61,1:02:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,so
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.61,1:02:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't get away from the desk
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.61,1:02:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,until I had 101
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.61,1:02:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,that kept me busy for weeks
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.61,1:02:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,by success you mean
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.48,1:02:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,personal, spiritual, or worldly
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.48,1:02:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,you know worldly success
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.48,1:02:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,interestingly enough
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.67,1:02:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,there's a couple of new books
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.67,1:02:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,out on success
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.86,1:02:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Gingrich's new book
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.86,1:02:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Five Principles
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.86,1:02:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,for a Successful Life
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.86,1:02:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,another interesting one
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.92,1:02:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,just came out
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.92,1:02:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,George Foreman's Knockout Entrepreneur
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.92,1:02:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,everybody familiar
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.15,1:02:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,with George Foreman's success story
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.15,1:02:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,how many are familiar with it
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.15,1:02:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah okay
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.53,1:02:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,well George Foreman of course
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.53,1:02:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,was a heavyweight champion of the world
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.53,1:02:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and he lost it
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.53,1:02:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,or gave up on it I forget
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.53,1:03:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and at age 45 I guess
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.53,1:03:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,he was broken
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.53,1:03:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,so I said George we're broke
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.53,1:03:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,you better go out and make some more money
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.53,1:03:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,George went back in the ring at age 45
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.53,1:03:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and re-won the world's heavyweight title
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.53,1:03:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,at age 45
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.69,1:03:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and then of course he went on to do
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.69,1:03:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,the Foreman Grill
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.69,1:03:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,which we have one at home
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.30,1:03:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,everybody has a Foreman Grill
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.30,1:03:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and he became a multi-millionaire
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.30,1:03:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,selling the Foreman Grill
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.30,1:03:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,we love our Foreman Grill
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.30,1:03:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't do hot dogs or anything
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.30,1:03:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,without your Foreman Grill
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.50,1:03:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,so
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.59,1:03:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,George Foreman's
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.59,1:03:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Knockout Entrepreneur
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.59,1:03:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,to re-win the
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.59,1:03:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,title at age 45
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.59,1:03:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,which in boxing is middle age
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.59,1:03:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,is impressive
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.71,1:03:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and then to go on to become
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.71,1:03:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,a millionaire
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.71,1:03:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,so there we're looking at success as winning
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.71,1:03:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and there
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.84,1:03:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,he won the championship
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.84,1:03:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and he won his wife's
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.84,1:03:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,return of her respect
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.84,1:04:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,that he wasn't a failure
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.84,1:04:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,he won the world's respect
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.84,1:04:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,everybody likes George Foreman
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.84,1:04:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,anybody here not like George Foreman?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.84,1:04:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,everybody likes George Foreman
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.84,1:04:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,so
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.92,1:04:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,likability and lovability
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.92,1:04:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,being very humanly human
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.92,1:04:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,so
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.13,1:04:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,to be successful we don't have to be
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.13,1:04:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,artificially perfect
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.13,1:04:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,very often the world loves us
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.13,1:04:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,for
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.13,1:04:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,our humanness and for our foibles
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.13,1:04:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and our nuttiness
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.13,1:04:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,success then is
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.13,1:04:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,can be limited
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.13,1:04:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,described as goal achievement
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.13,1:04:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,to do this
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.65,1:04:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,project that I had here
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.88,1:04:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to do
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.88,1:04:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,101 ways to success
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.88,1:04:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,so I
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.88,1:04:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't achieve the goal
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.88,1:04:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,until I got to 101
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.88,1:04:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and along the way
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.00,1:04:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I got a couple dozen
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.00,1:04:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that I thought about
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.00,1:05:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and decided I didn't like too well
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.23,1:05:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and threw them away
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.28,1:05:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and went to the next
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.32,1:05:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,today's lecture is a success
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.32,1:05:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,in that I achieved
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.32,1:05:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,putting together 101 ways
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.32,1:05:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and then I calibrated them all
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.32,1:05:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,with my arm etc
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.32,1:05:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,success is the world's view
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.32,1:05:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,as being prominent
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.32,1:05:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,this is the predominant
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.32,1:05:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,idea of success in today's world
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.32,1:05:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,is to be prominent
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.32,1:05:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,to be a media attraction
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.32,1:05:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and to reach celebrity status
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.32,1:05:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,success
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.32,1:05:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,as prominence
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.32,1:05:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and media attraction
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.32,1:05:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and celebrity status
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.42,1:05:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,so
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.42,1:05:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,today the world is dominated
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.44,1:05:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,by the media
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.44,1:05:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're successful
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.44,1:05:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,if all the programs want you on there
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.44,1:05:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,to be a guest on their program
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.44,1:05:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and you feel like a success
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.63,1:05:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,you feel like a success
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.63,1:05:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,so there is a downward side
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.63,1:05:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,to media attention
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.63,1:05:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,it sucks you in
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.63,1:06:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,without you realizing it
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.09,1:06:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,people say oh it hasn't affected me
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.09,1:06:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,oh yes it does
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.09,1:06:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,being the big star on a TV show
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.09,1:06:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,does affect you
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.21,1:06:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.21,1:06:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been on a number of them back in New York
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.21,1:06:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.25,1:06:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,there's a peculiarity to it
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.25,1:06:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,unless you've been a guest
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.25,1:06:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,on some big name
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.25,1:06:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,show you don't appreciate it
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.25,1:06:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,how many people have been a guest on a big time show
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.25,1:06:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and many people here
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.25,1:06:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,not too many
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.01,1:06:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,well anyway somebody knows somebody
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.01,1:06:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and you get invited to be
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.01,1:06:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,on a certain show
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.01,1:06:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I forget the names of them all
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.40,1:06:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,they were all back in New York
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.40,1:06:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,so it's very interesting
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.40,1:06:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,you drive all the way to New York City
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.40,1:06:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you go up
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.40,1:06:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,in these giant buildings
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.40,1:06:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and you go up to the level where the studio is
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.40,1:06:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.40,1:06:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the studio takes a whole level
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.40,1:06:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,of a huge building
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.40,1:06:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,probably covers half an acre
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.40,1:07:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I think
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.40,1:07:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and of course the makeup is waiting for you
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.40,1:07:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,so you get there and all of a sudden
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.40,1:07:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,everybody's flying around you
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.40,1:07:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and they're fixing your face all up
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.40,1:07:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and painting your ear lobes and all this
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.40,1:07:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and you get all this attention
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.40,1:07:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,then you go on the talk show
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.40,1:07:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I forget the name of them all
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.40,1:07:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Barbara Walters
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.55,1:07:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I was on hers a couple of times
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.55,1:07:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,a number of shows like that
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.55,1:07:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,so anyway you're the big star of the moment
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.55,1:07:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're the focus of everybody
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.55,1:07:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,the wardrobe people are there
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.55,1:07:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,every little thing is absolutely perfect
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.55,1:07:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,the Klieg lights go on
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.55,1:07:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and now you're Mr. Big
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.55,1:07:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,70 million people are watching you at this moment
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.55,1:07:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,70 million people
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.55,1:07:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,are watching every little twitch of your nose
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.55,1:07:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and Barbara Walters
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.55,1:07:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,a couple of times
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.55,1:07:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,other big name shows but anyway
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.55,1:07:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,so for the moment you're somebody
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.55,1:07:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,makeup makes you somebody
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.55,1:07:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and the Klieg lights go on
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.55,1:07:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and these studios are huge
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.55,1:08:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,they're really giant places
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.55,1:08:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and all of a sudden
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.55,1:08:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the show comes to an end
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.88,1:08:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,all the lights go out
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.88,1:08:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,everybody leaves
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.88,1:08:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and there you are all alone
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.88,1:08:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,in a half-acre studio
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.88,1:08:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,with nobody there but you
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.88,1:08:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,where the hell is the door
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.88,1:08:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,how do you get out of here
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.01,1:08:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I could not find somebody
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.01,1:08:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,to let me out
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.01,1:08:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally find a janitor
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.01,1:08:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I said how do you get out of here
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.01,1:08:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,so here you are
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.52,1:08:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,charged up
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.52,1:08:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,the adrenaline
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.52,1:08:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,all the cortisol and all the kind of hormones
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.52,1:08:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,veins etc
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.68,1:08:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,you're Mr. Big for the moment
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.68,1:08:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,you come down this huge building
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.68,1:08:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Rockefeller Center and there you are
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.68,1:08:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,you come down you get off the elevator
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.68,1:08:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and you step out into the street
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.68,1:08:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and there's this huge feeling of
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.68,1:08:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,loss, of drop
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.88,1:08:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,from being somebody
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.88,1:08:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,from being it
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.88,1:08:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,you're nobody
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.42,1:09:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,from being the ultimate it
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.42,1:09:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,you're no one
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.22,1:09:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,there aren't 70 million people
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.22,1:09:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,getting wrapped by you
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.31,1:09:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,so I understood why
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.05,1:09:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,why the
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.52,1:09:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,why the people in entertainment business
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.52,1:09:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and certain aspects of the entertainment business
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.52,1:09:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,are so prone to drugs
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.52,1:09:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,because that drop is awful
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.60,1:09:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,imagine your cortisone
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.65,1:09:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,your adrenaline
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.65,1:09:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,everything is way up here
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.65,1:09:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,suddenly it pulls the rug out from under you
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.65,1:09:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,suddenly you're nothing
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.65,1:09:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,you're nobody
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.65,1:09:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,nobody cares about you
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.68,1:09:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,nobody even says hello
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.78,1:09:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,that sudden drop is sickening
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.78,1:09:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I get why all the rock stars
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.78,1:09:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and all them
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.78,1:09:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,get into drugs because
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.78,1:09:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,at the end of the program you can't get off that high
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.78,1:09:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,you want to keep the high going
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.78,1:09:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,so I had greater sympathy
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.78,1:09:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,for people in the media
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.78,1:09:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,who get into drugs because I can see
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.78,1:09:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,they can't stand that
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.85,1:09:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,adrenaline rush
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.85,1:10:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,the cortisone shooting out
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.85,1:10:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,the endorphins shooting out
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.85,1:10:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and suddenly they pull the plug on you
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.85,1:10:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,suddenly you're nobody
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.85,1:10:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,you got nothing and all your hormones collapse
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.85,1:10:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.88,1:10:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you're a nothing and a nobody
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.88,1:10:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,so I understood instantly
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.88,1:10:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,why they have to keep that high going
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.88,1:10:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,so typically in that particular culture
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.88,1:10:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,after the program is over
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.88,1:10:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you meet over at somebody's house
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.88,1:10:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and everybody is high
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.88,1:10:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you stay high until 3 or 4 in the morning
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.88,1:10:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,so I got off being any
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.88,1:10:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,any kind of moral
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.88,1:10:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,being moral about it
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.88,1:10:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I could just understand it
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.88,1:10:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,so one thing about the willingness
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.88,1:10:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and the decision to be loving towards all of life
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.88,1:10:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and all of its expressions
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.88,1:10:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,is you achieve a greater understanding
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.88,1:10:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you find that you're not prone
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.88,1:10:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,to right and wrong
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.88,1:10:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you're no longer subject to
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.88,1:10:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,criticizing people and putting them down
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.88,1:10:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,what you're interested in is
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.88,1:10:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,understanding them
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.88,1:10:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,when they come out of the prisons
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.94,1:10:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and they continue the crime
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.94,1:11:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the same as before they went in
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.94,1:11:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of condemning them
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.94,1:11:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,you begin to understand them
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.01,1:11:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,for them there is no other life
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.01,1:11:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,there is no other life
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.01,1:11:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,except going back to mugging
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.01,1:11:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and drugs and pedophilia
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.01,1:11:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and whatever put them there in the first place
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.01,1:11:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,because that is their life
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.81,1:11:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,so we're looking more at success
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.81,1:11:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,as happiness
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.90,1:11:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and one way
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.93,1:11:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,to achieve success
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.93,1:11:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,one attribute
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.93,1:11:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,is to build a good karma balance
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.93,1:11:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,what does that mean
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.93,1:11:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,it means you have like a deposit
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.93,1:11:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,in a savings account
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.93,1:11:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,everybody has a karma savings account
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.93,1:11:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,you ever know that
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.93,1:11:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,see that's true
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.96,1:11:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,everybody has a karma
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.96,1:11:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,savings account
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.31,1:11:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the little bug that you didn't step on
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.31,1:11:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a little bug
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.02,1:11:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,adds to your positive karma
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.02,1:12:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,savings account
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.23,1:12:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and the next time
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.78,1:12:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,a pot falls off the top of a building
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.78,1:12:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,it'll miss you instead of hitting you
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.78,1:12:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,in the top of the head
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.68,1:12:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,it doesn't take great achievements
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.68,1:12:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't have to save the life
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.68,1:12:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,of thousands of people
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.31,1:12:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,by inventing penicillin or something
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.44,1:12:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,all of life and all of its expressions
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.44,1:12:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,builds up a positive karma balance
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.44,1:12:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and when you need it
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.44,1:12:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,it's there, it's like a savings account
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.44,1:12:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and I've had a number of
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.44,1:12:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,many occurrences in my life
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.44,1:12:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,that cannot be explained
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.44,1:12:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,by any kind of logic whatsoever
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.84,1:12:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,being out in the middle of nowhere
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.84,1:12:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I myself was lost
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.84,1:12:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't even know where the hell I was
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.84,1:12:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and I pulled the truck over
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.14,1:12:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,in the middle of nowhere
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.36,1:12:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and nobody I knew within hundreds of miles
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.36,1:12:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I got a phone call
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.36,1:12:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a flat tire
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.36,1:12:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and I pulled the truck over by the side of the road
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.36,1:13:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and all of a sudden
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.36,1:13:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,off the little road itself
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.36,1:13:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,a car pulls over
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.36,1:13:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and pulls right over in front of my truck
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.36,1:13:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's an old buddy from school
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.56,1:13:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Dave look at you
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.56,1:13:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,you got a flat
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.35,1:13:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,can I help you
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.35,1:13:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,that happened to me a number of times
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.35,1:13:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,one time I was on one of these crazy
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.35,1:13:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,loop-de-loop things on the way to the airport
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.35,1:13:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and the truck broke down
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.35,1:13:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,in the middle of all these loop-de-loops you know
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.35,1:13:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm flat
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.35,1:13:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really in a bad way
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.35,1:13:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and this guy pulls next to me
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.35,1:13:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,he says can I help you buddy
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.35,1:13:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I got a flat
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.35,1:13:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,he says don't worry
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.35,1:13:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,this guy who was a complete stranger
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.35,1:13:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,took the tire off
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.35,1:13:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,threw it in the back of his pickup
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.35,1:13:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,went down to the loop-de-loop
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.35,1:13:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,went to a garage
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.35,1:13:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,got it fixed
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.35,1:13:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,went back through the curly Q8 loop-de-loops
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.82,1:13:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and came back to my car
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.89,1:13:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and put it on my car for me
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.89,1:14:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,no
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.89,1:14:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,that's positive karma balance
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.72,1:14:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,in other words
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.72,1:14:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the goodness that you've radiated towards all of life
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.72,1:14:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,to the best of your ability
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.72,1:14:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,is not like a savings account
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.72,1:14:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and when you need it
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.72,1:14:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,it's there to draw on
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.01,1:14:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and you never know
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.01,1:14:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,when you're gonna need it
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.01,1:14:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,lightning strikes without warning
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.14,1:14:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.14,1:14:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,so
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.30,1:14:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,when your life is hanging in the balance
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.30,1:14:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,or something about your life is hanging in the balance
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.30,1:14:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,if you have a positive karma balance
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.30,1:14:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,it swings the result
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.30,1:14:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,in a favorable direction
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.30,1:14:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and if you have a negative karma balance
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.30,1:14:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,it swings the
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.30,1:14:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,pendulum in a negative direction
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.30,1:14:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,so
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.32,1:14:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,my advice is to always keep a
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.32,1:14:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,positive karma balance
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.32,1:14:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,what do they call this
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.15,1:14:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,where you do a good favor for people
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.15,1:14:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,for no reason whatsoever
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.39,1:14:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,what do they call it
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.60,1:15:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,random acts of kindness
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.15,1:15:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,yes
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.27,1:15:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,the laws of random acts of kindness
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.27,1:15:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,that's really the operation
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.27,1:15:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,out of which it works
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.27,1:15:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,by constantly building a positive
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.27,1:15:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,karma bank account
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.27,1:15:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't know when you're gonna need it
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.72,1:15:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,you may not need it
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.72,1:15:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,to the last five seconds of life
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.92,1:15:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,say I don't need it
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.92,1:15:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,wait till you get to the end
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.92,1:15:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and then let me know
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.52,1:15:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,we've got three minutes
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.52,1:15:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,oh my god I better hurry up
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.52,1:15:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,oh my god
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.10,1:15:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,success is being important and famous
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.10,1:15:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and a celebrity
Dialogue: 0,1:15:43.10,1:15:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,success is happiness
