Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.97,1:25:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.77,1:25:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,we're pleased therefore
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.77,1:25:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,with incremental goals
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.77,1:25:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't have to become the star of the show
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.77,1:25:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.77,1:25:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,the fact that you're making progress
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.77,1:25:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,is sufficient
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.06,1:25:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,we said that it's a way
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.06,1:25:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,success is a way of being in the world
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.06,1:25:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a way in which you are
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.06,1:25:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,the way in which you are
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.22,1:25:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,tends to radiate a certain energy
Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.22,1:25:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and that certain energy tends to influence
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.22,1:25:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,things that are around you
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.22,1:25:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,so that spiritually advanced people
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.60,1:25:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,will experience the world differently
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.60,1:25:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,than people who are not
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.60,1:25:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I can remember there was a phase in my life
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.60,1:25:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,that I went through a very high state
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.60,1:25:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how I survived the body
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.60,1:25:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and everywhere I went
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.60,1:25:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,people broke into
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.60,1:25:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,gleeful happiness
Dialogue: 0,1:25:48.60,1:25:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and I had an apartment in New York City
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.67,1:25:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and I would make my rounds in the morning
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.67,1:25:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the various doormen of the various buildings
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.67,1:25:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and the various shops
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.67,1:25:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,everybody would light up
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.85,1:26:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,as you came
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.92,1:26:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,to their attention
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.92,1:26:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,they just became lit up
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.92,1:26:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and not because of who you are personally
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.11,1:26:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,so it's got nothing to do with you as a person
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.11,1:26:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,but something about that energy
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.11,1:26:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,uplifted everyone
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.11,1:26:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,so all the doormen look forward
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.11,1:26:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,to seeing me make my
Dialogue: 0,1:26:17.11,1:26:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,morning rounds
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.11,1:26:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and the various stores
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.11,1:26:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,that I would go in
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.11,1:26:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,so you tended to uplift
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.11,1:26:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,all that come into contact with you
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.11,1:26:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,so success
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.75,1:26:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,is not what you do
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.75,1:26:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,but what you have become
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.75,1:26:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,aha
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.09,1:26:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,it isn't what you do
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.15,1:26:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,it isn't what you have
Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.15,1:26:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,it's what you become
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.31,1:26:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,it's what you are
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.72,1:26:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,what you are
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.72,1:26:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,it transmits that energy
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.72,1:26:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,of other people
Dialogue: 0,1:26:52.72,1:26:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,of feeling friendly and confident
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.72,1:26:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and more entitled to
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.85,1:26:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,give you the truth than a falsehood
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.85,1:27:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,to be loving towards you
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.07,1:27:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,than unloving
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.07,1:27:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,so
Dialogue: 0,1:27:05.56,1:27:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,that's something to be thankful for
Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.56,1:27:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,it isn't what I do
Dialogue: 0,1:27:09.56,1:27:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,it isn't what I have
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.56,1:27:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,it's what I've become
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.56,1:27:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,so what you are
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.56,1:27:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,is already a guarantee
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.56,1:27:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,of success
Dialogue: 0,1:27:19.56,1:27:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,your functions then will follow
Dialogue: 0,1:27:21.56,1:27:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,what you are
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.68,1:27:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,what you are will determine
Dialogue: 0,1:27:25.68,1:27:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,what your judgments and your decisions are
Dialogue: 0,1:27:27.68,1:27:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and the answers you get about
Dialogue: 0,1:27:29.68,1:27:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,certain things
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.76,1:27:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and so
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.76,1:27:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,if in doubt
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.76,1:27:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,you can find somebody with whom
Dialogue: 0,1:27:37.76,1:27:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,you can do the simple test
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.76,1:27:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,of truth versus falsehood
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.07,1:27:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,thankful rather than prideful
Dialogue: 0,1:27:44.07,1:27:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you God for all the gifts
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.07,1:27:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,of this life
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.07,1:27:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,so the very successful
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.07,1:27:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,people I've known
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.43,1:27:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,in this lifetime
Dialogue: 0,1:27:54.43,1:27:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,have all been very modest
Dialogue: 0,1:27:56.43,1:27:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,very modest people
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.43,1:28:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,you know worth enormous amounts of money
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.43,1:28:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and etc etc
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.43,1:28:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and very modest
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.43,1:28:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,modest as a person
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.46,1:28:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,so we are interested then
Dialogue: 0,1:28:08.46,1:28:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,in incremental goals
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.46,1:28:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't have to become a worldly success overnight
Dialogue: 0,1:28:12.46,1:28:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a result of basic attitudes
Dialogue: 0,1:28:14.46,1:28:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,there is also
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.46,1:28:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,a certain determination
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.46,1:28:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,to achieve certain standards
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.56,1:28:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,determination to
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.56,1:28:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,give the best lecture I can give today
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.56,1:28:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,you know the determination
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.56,1:28:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,may not be the best lecture I can give today
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.56,1:28:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,but as far as my intention is
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.56,1:28:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,to get across certain basic things
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.56,1:28:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,in both the verbal
Dialogue: 0,1:28:34.56,1:28:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and the non-verbal
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.56,1:28:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I also trust that the
Dialogue: 0,1:28:39.77,1:28:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,non-verbal energy field
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.77,1:28:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,transmits itself
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.77,1:28:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and then is acquired
Dialogue: 0,1:28:45.77,1:28:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,by the listener
Dialogue: 0,1:28:47.77,1:28:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,by virtue of the
Dialogue: 0,1:28:49.77,1:28:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,listener's agreement
Dialogue: 0,1:28:51.77,1:28:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,by your agreement
Dialogue: 0,1:28:53.77,1:28:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and you have agreed
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.77,1:28:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,to pick up from the energy field
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.77,1:28:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,of this consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:28:59.77,1:29:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,the radiance of that
Dialogue: 0,1:29:01.77,1:29:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,which has been transmitted down
Dialogue: 0,1:29:03.77,1:29:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,through the centuries
Dialogue: 0,1:29:05.77,1:29:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and which you will then transmit to others
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.77,1:29:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,so the thing to be happy about
Dialogue: 0,1:29:09.77,1:29:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,is that you have become
Dialogue: 0,1:29:11.77,1:29:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,an asset to the world
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.77,1:29:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,that you have
Dialogue: 0,1:29:15.77,1:29:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,all the people in this room
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.77,1:29:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,have become an asset to the world
Dialogue: 0,1:29:19.77,1:29:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,not everyone can say they are an asset
Dialogue: 0,1:29:21.77,1:29:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,to this world
Dialogue: 0,1:29:23.77,1:29:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I can think of a few people right now
Dialogue: 0,1:29:29.77,1:29:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,but what a gift that is
Dialogue: 0,1:29:31.77,1:29:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,so as you can see
Dialogue: 0,1:29:33.84,1:29:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,out of that you become thankful
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.84,1:29:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,you become that
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.60,1:29:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,which is a gift to your children
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.60,1:29:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,to your parents
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.60,1:29:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,to your society
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.60,1:29:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,to your neighborhood
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.60,1:29:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,just by the fact that you live there
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.60,1:29:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the crime rate has gone down
Dialogue: 0,1:29:50.76,1:29:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,would you believe that
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.56,1:29:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,the fact that you live where you live
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.90,1:29:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,accounts for the fact
Dialogue: 0,1:29:58.90,1:30:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,of a reduction of the crime rate
Dialogue: 0,1:30:00.90,1:30:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,where you live
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.90,1:30:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,where you live
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.52,1:30:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,the crime rate is already reduced
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.52,1:30:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,because of the radiance
Dialogue: 0,1:30:11.52,1:30:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,that you emit from your aura
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.52,1:30:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,so that gives you great respect
Dialogue: 0,1:30:15.60,1:30:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,for the aura
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.60,1:30:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,down through the millennia
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.52,1:30:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,down through the centuries
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.52,1:30:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the great wisdom
Dialogue: 0,1:30:24.68,1:30:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,which originates with divinity
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.97,1:30:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,has radiated down
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.97,1:30:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,through the great spiritual teachers
Dialogue: 0,1:30:30.97,1:30:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,etc
Dialogue: 0,1:30:33.03,1:30:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and is now
Dialogue: 0,1:30:35.31,1:30:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,characteristic of my aura
Dialogue: 0,1:30:38.25,1:30:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,that which I am radiates peace
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.25,1:30:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and success to the world
Dialogue: 0,1:30:42.25,1:30:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,let's all say that
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.60,1:30:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,that which I am radiates peace and success to the world
Dialogue: 0,1:30:47.60,1:30:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,that which I am
Dialogue: 0,1:30:49.60,1:30:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,radiates peace
Dialogue: 0,1:30:51.60,1:30:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and success to the world
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.60,1:30:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen
Dialogue: 0,1:30:56.35,1:30:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,ok, you don't have to do anything
Dialogue: 0,1:30:58.35,1:31:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not what you do
Dialogue: 0,1:31:00.35,1:31:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,there's all kinds of do-gooders
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.35,1:31:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,God help me
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.90,1:31:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,California is really bad for do-gooders
Dialogue: 0,1:31:06.90,1:31:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I think
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.55,1:31:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,they're lurking around every corner
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.55,1:31:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,eat this, don't eat that
Dialogue: 0,1:31:14.64,1:31:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,don't smoke a cigarette
Dialogue: 0,1:31:16.64,1:31:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,oh my God, geez
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.64,1:31:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,it's worse than murder
Dialogue: 0,1:31:20.64,1:31:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,murder is ok, but smoking a cigarette
Dialogue: 0,1:31:24.30,1:31:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,good God
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.30,1:31:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the ultimate crime of mankind
Dialogue: 0,1:31:32.46,1:31:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,World War II
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.46,1:31:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,was won by camel cigarettes
Dialogue: 0,1:31:39.27,1:31:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,you didn't know that
Dialogue: 0,1:31:41.27,1:31:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,every lifeboat had a carton of camels
Dialogue: 0,1:31:43.27,1:31:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,in there
Dialogue: 0,1:31:45.27,1:31:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,if we didn't see
Dialogue: 0,1:31:47.27,1:31:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,we'd pretty soon run out of smoke
Dialogue: 0,1:31:49.27,1:31:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,so we'd raid the lifeboats
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.27,1:31:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and steal the carton of camels
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.27,1:31:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,they were 10 cents a pack
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.27,1:31:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,anyway, so that was a different generation
Dialogue: 0,1:31:57.27,1:31:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,this generation of course
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.27,1:32:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,is more pure
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.94,1:32:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,when I go to California
Dialogue: 0,1:32:07.55,1:32:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,they say
Dialogue: 0,1:32:09.55,1:32:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,you're going amongst the pure
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.65,1:32:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,you get a little California halo
Dialogue: 0,1:32:19.65,1:32:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,this is California
Dialogue: 0,1:32:21.88,1:32:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,what happened to my slides?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.88,1:32:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,oh
Dialogue: 0,1:32:26.32,1:32:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,well
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.88,1:32:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,humor is one of the best teachers there is
Dialogue: 0,1:32:30.88,1:32:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,so humor
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.88,1:32:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't take yourself too seriously
Dialogue: 0,1:32:34.88,1:32:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,it seemed like a good idea at the time
Dialogue: 0,1:32:36.88,1:32:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you say so
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.88,1:32:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,it seemed like a good idea at the time
Dialogue: 0,1:32:40.88,1:32:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet all our money on a certain stock
Dialogue: 0,1:32:42.88,1:32:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and of course it collapsed within 72 hours
Dialogue: 0,1:32:44.88,1:32:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and we lost a million
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.88,1:32:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,oh well
Dialogue: 0,1:32:48.88,1:32:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,on the other hand
Dialogue: 0,1:32:50.88,1:32:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you bet on it
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.88,1:32:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and it went up and you made a million
Dialogue: 0,1:32:54.88,1:32:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you're thankful rather than prideful
Dialogue: 0,1:32:56.88,1:32:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't say well I made a good decision
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.88,1:33:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,no
Dialogue: 0,1:33:00.88,1:33:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you didn't make a good decision
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.88,1:33:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the world made a decision
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.88,1:33:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,why a stock goes up
Dialogue: 0,1:33:06.88,1:33:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,or a stock goes down
Dialogue: 0,1:33:08.88,1:33:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,is due to millions of factors
Dialogue: 0,1:33:10.88,1:33:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,so anyway
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.10,1:33:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,we're satisfied with progress
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.10,1:33:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,incremental goals
Dialogue: 0,1:33:17.10,1:33:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,progress rather than perfection
Dialogue: 0,1:33:19.15,1:33:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and this progress is a result of
Dialogue: 0,1:33:21.15,1:33:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,basic attitudes that we have
Dialogue: 0,1:33:23.15,1:33:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,accumulated by good
Dialogue: 0,1:33:25.15,1:33:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and positive merit
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.71,1:33:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,one thing is determination
Dialogue: 0,1:33:29.71,1:33:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,determination to do a good job
Dialogue: 0,1:33:31.71,1:33:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,another thing we call is
Dialogue: 0,1:33:34.11,1:33:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,willpower or grit
Dialogue: 0,1:33:36.47,1:33:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,we visualize our goals
Dialogue: 0,1:33:38.47,1:33:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and chip away incrementally
